An absolutely beautiful story and the only published novel from Oscar Wilde, this follows the story of a beautiful young man named Dorian Grey. He has his portrait painted by a well to do artist. The artist is completely infatuated with him btw. The artist introduces him to a different artist who convinces Dorian that the only thing worth a lick in this world is beauty. Dorian becomes obsessed with this idea and sells his soul so that he can remain beautiful while the portrait of him ages.